            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Μάαρκος Γράνιος Μαάρκου Ἡρακ(λέων<certainty match="preceding-sibling::node()" locus="value"/> <lb n="2"/>Διόδοτος Σήιος Γαίου καὶ Γναίου <lb n="3"/>Ἀπολλώνιος Λαίλιος Κοίντου <lb n="4"/>Πρέπων Ἄλλιος Μαάρκου <lb n="5"/>Νίκανδρος Ῥασέννιος Μαάρκου <lb n="6"/>Δία Ἐλευθέριον ἀνέθηκαν </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Granius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibertus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Her</abbr><ex>as</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Diodotus Seius <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Cn</abbr><ex>aei</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>Apollonius Laelius <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Prepon Alleius <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/>Nicandrus <expan><abbr>n<am>n</am></abbr><ex>us</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ervus</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/>Iovem Leiberum <expan><abbr>statuer</abbr><ex>unt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Am Zeilenende von Z. 1 wurde Ἡρᾶς statt Ἡρακ(λέων?) gelesen. Die Qualität der Abbildungen ließ eine genaue Nachprüfung der Lesungen nicht zu.</p>
            </div>
